---
import InnerPage from '../../layouts/InnerPage.astro';
---
<InnerPage
  title="Blog | Selling Your House in Wichita KS | Jacob Buys Your House"
  description="Helpful, straight-talk articles for Wichita homeowners thinking about selling — inherited properties, as-is sales, foreclosure, and more."
  heroImage="/situations/blog-hero.jpg"
  heroTitle="Wichita Home Selling Resources"
  heroSub="Straight talk about selling your house in the Wichita area — no fluff, no sales pitches."
>

  <style>
    .blog-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px; margin: 28px 0; }
    .blog-card {
      display: block; text-decoration: none;
      background: white; border: 1px solid #e0e8f0;
      border-radius: 18px; overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 14px rgba(58,161,248,.08);
      transition: all .2s;
    }
    .blog-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 10px 36px rgba(58,161,248,.16); }
    .blog-card-img {
      height: 200px;
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      position: relative;
    }
    .blog-card-img::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent 50%, rgba(0,0,0,.45) 100%);
    }
    .blog-card-tag {
      position: absolute; top: 14px; left: 14px; z-index: 1;
      background: #e87122; color: white;
      font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 6px;
    }
    .blog-card-body { padding: 22px 24px 24px; }
    .blog-meta { font-size: 12.5px; color: #888; margin-bottom: 10px; display: flex; gap: 12px; }
    .blog-card-body h2 { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 800; color: #1d1d1d; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.4; }
    .blog-card-body p { font-size: 14px; color: #555; line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .blog-read-more { font-size: 13.5px; font-weight: 700; color: #3aa1f8; }
    @media(max-width:600px){ .blog-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

    .blog-cta-strip {
      background: #e8f5ff; border: 1px solid #cce8ff;
      border-radius: 16px; padding: 28px 32px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 20px; margin-top: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .blog-cta-strip p { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: #0d5fa0; margin: 0; }
    .blog-cta-strip a { background: #e87122; color: white; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; white-space: nowrap; }
    .blog-cta-strip a:hover { background: #c45a12; }
  </style>

  <h2>Latest Articles</h2>
  <p>We publish practical guides for Wichita homeowners — whether you're leaning toward a cash sale or just trying to understand your options. New posts added regularly.</p>

  <div class="blog-grid">
    <a href="/blog/sell-inherited-house-wichita-ks" class="blog-card">
      <div class="blog-card-img" style="background-image:url('/situations/blog-inherited.jpg')">
        <span class="blog-card-tag">Inherited Property</span>
      </div>
      <div class="blog-card-body">
        <div class="blog-meta"><span>📅 March 2026</span><span>⏱ 5 min read</span></div>
        <h2>How to Sell an Inherited House in Wichita, KS — Without the Headache</h2>
        <p>Inherited a property in Wichita? Here's what probate looks like, your three main options, and how to get through it without losing your mind.</p>
        <span class="blog-read-more">Read article →</span>
      </div>
    </a>
    <a href="/blog/sell-house-as-is-wichita-ks" class="blog-card">
      <div class="blog-card-img" style="background-image:url('/situations/blog-as-is.jpg')">
        <span class="blog-card-tag">Selling As-Is</span>
      </div>
      <div class="blog-card-body">
        <div class="blog-meta"><span>📅 March 2026</span><span>⏱ 4 min read</span></div>
        <h2>How to Sell a House As-Is in Wichita, KS (And What to Expect)</h2>
        <p>What does "as-is" actually mean? Who buys them, how offers are calculated, and whether it's the right move for your situation.</p>
        <span class="blog-read-more">Read article →</span>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>

  <div class="blog-cta-strip">
    <p>💡 Have a question about your specific situation? Jacob answers his own phone.</p>
    <a href="tel:3163683344">Call (316) 368-3344</a>
  </div>

</InnerPage>
